name: CDOT Traffic and GHG, A Comparative Analysis
description: A comparative analysis examining rates of traffic and greenhouse gas emissions between public and private transit in Colorado. Write-up (will be) available on Medium!

name: An Exploratory Analysis of US Census and HUD data
description: An exploratory analysis of Homelessness in the US and the rates of vacant homes according to US dept. of HUD and the US Census. Visualizes rates of homelessness across many different demographic dimensions (race, gender, location, more).

name: Investigating causes of Heart Disease, Hypothesis Testing
description: An analysis examining and determining causes of Heart Disease using hypothesis testing implemented in Python. Performed using the UC Irving's Machine Learning dataset on Heart Disease.

name: Collecting Colorado Housing listings from Craigslist
description: A webscraping project that collected available information from Craigslist Housing posts across all Colorado sites. Generated datasets to use analysis to decide on a new place to move to in Colorado.

name: Code Exercises
description: All the code exercises that I've completed and kept the corresponding scripts for. Includes: CodeWars, Leetcode, and more.

name: Palettes.jl
description: A tool-kit, built using the Julia programming language, for creating Palettes of related colors or just generating randomized colors.
